body_html: This is a recent change in onnx onnx/onnx@f4acf28 that removed the in-place annotations in onnx level. This change is not included in our last onnx release but we have made the corresponding change to pytorch master to pair with onnx master. So If you can install onnx from the onnx master, this issue should be solved.
